tcp: use tcp_jiffies32 to feed tp->snd_cwnd_stamp

Use tcp_jiffies32 instead of tcp_time_stamp to feed
tp->snd_cwnd_stamp.

tcp_time_stamp will soon be a litle bit more expensive
than simply reading 'jiffies'.

